OL,3,CConservative MP Mark Logan defects to
OL,4,CLabour
OL,6,FFormer Conservative MP Mark Logan has
OL,7,Fsaid he is defecting to the Labour
OL,8,Fparty.
OL,10,FThe MP was elected for Bolton North
OL,11,FEast in 2019, but says he is now
OL,12,Fquitting the Tories and is urging
OL,13,Fpeople to vote for Sir Kier Starmer on
OL,14,F4 July.
OL,16,FIn recent months he has been a fierce
OL,17,Fcritic of the government's policy on
OL,18,FGaza, and says the Tories are
OL,19,F"unrecognisable" from the party he
OL,20,Fjoined a decade ago.
