OL,3,CConservative MP Mark Logan defects to
OL,4,CLabour
OL,6,FThe 40-year-old said his application
OL,7,Fto join Labour was "going in today",
OL,8,Fdescribing Sir Keir Starmer's party as
OL,9,Fhaving been on a "journey" and now
OL,10,Foffering "centrist politics".
OL,12,FHe said: "I believe, as a politician,
OL,13,Fit's incumbent upon me to be able to
OL,14,Fsay, to look people in the eyes in
OL,15,FBolton and say that I believe that a
OL,16,FLabour government is going to serve
OL,17,Fyou better, your interests better,
OL,18,Fit's going to be better for your
OL,19,Fpockets, it's better for the economy,
OL,20,Fit's going to be better for the UK."
