OL,3,CConservative MP Mark Logan defects to
OL,4,CLabour
OL,6,FReferencing Gaza and the impact of
OL,7,Finflation on Bolton, Mr Logan said he
OL,8,Fis standing down at this election and
OL,9,FLabour has already chosen a candidate
OL,10,Ffor his former constituency.
OL,12,FIn a "personal statement" written just
OL,13,Fbefore parliament dissolved on
OL,14,FThursday, Mr Logan referred to
OL,15,FLabour's 1997 election anthem Things
OL,16,FCan Only Get Better.
OL,18,F"Labour is back, and given how things
OL,19,Fhave been, I believe things can only
OL,20,Fget better", he said.
