OL,3,CConservative MP Mark Logan defects to
OL,4,CLabour
OL,6,FExplaining his decision to support
OL,7,FLabour, he said in a statement: "We
OL,8,Fneed renewed enthusiasm and optimism
OL,9,Fin both tone and in policy, and I
OL,10,Fbelieve that we are already seeing
OL,11,Fthis through Keir Starmer and the
OL,12,Fteam."
OL,14,FIn February Mr Logan broke ranks from
OL,15,Fhis own party to call for an immediate
OL,16,Fceasefire in the Gaza conflict, saying
OL,17,FIsrael had "gone too far".
